            <p class="mb-4">We print social distancing floor decals that guide customers through your space safely and clearly. Floor decals are a uniquely effective safety tool because they communicate directly at foot level, right where people are naturally looking as they walk. A floor decal placed at the entrance of a checkout line, in front of a service counter, or at a waiting area immediately tells customers where to stand without any verbal instruction from staff. We have printed floor decals for grocery stores, pharmacies, banks, gyms, and many other high traffic businesses throughout Joliet, Shorewood, and Will County.</p>
            <p class="mb-4">Our floor decals are printed on heavy duty laminated adhesive vinyl that is specifically designed for foot traffic applications. The surface laminate is slip resistant and rated for both smooth commercial flooring and low pile carpet. The adhesive bonds securely to the floor during use but releases cleanly when you peel it up, leaving no sticky residue behind. This makes our floor decals a practical, reusable solution that you can apply for an event or a busy season and remove when conditions change without any damage to your flooring.</p>
            <p>We print floor decals in any size, shape, and design. Standard circular floor decals with directional arrows or "please wait here" messaging are the most popular, but we also print custom shaped floor decals with logos, brand colors, and custom messaging. We serve businesses in Joliet, Shorewood, Crest Hill, Romeoville, and across the entire Chicagoland area. Call us at (815) 349 8600 to order your floor decals today.</p>
        </x-sections.card-image-with-text>

        <x-sections.card-image-with-text
            image="/images/corona-virus-signs/top5pct-coronavirus-stickers-joliet-shorewood-crest-hill.jpg"
